
=== Attribute ==============================================

group_column_width: <size>              # set group column width (default: 48)
wns_width: <size>                       # set WNS column width   (default: 12)
tns_width: <size>                       # set TNS column width   (default: 12)
nvp_width: <size>                       # set NVP column width   (default: 6)

auto_resize_column_width: <bool>        # default: true

=== Path Choose (Violation Report) =========================    

p:<type>:<group>:<path>:<rid>           # use regular expression to choose path

- type  : violation type
- group : regular expression pattern for group specify
- path  : regular expression pattern for path specify
- rid   : report ID (value: l-left, r-right, a-all)

=== Path Operation (Summary Report) ========================

<inst_path> u:[condition]:<ugroup>      # move to user-defined group if condition match

- condition format : <target><operation><value>
    - target     : act, slk
    - operation  : >, <, ==, >=, <=
    - value type : float

- ugroup : user group name

=== Group Choose (Summary Report) ==========================

g:<type>:<group>:<rid>                  # use regular expression to choose group
                                            
- type  : violation type
- group : regular expression pattern for group specify
- rid   : report ID (value: l-left, r-right, d-diff)

=== Group Operation (Summary Report) =======================

<group> t:<tag>                         # add group tag
<group> s:[condition]:<status>          # add group status (one-character tag)
<group> m:[condition]:<message>         # add group comment message

- condition format : <target><operation><value>
    - target     : wns, tns, nvp
    - operation  : >, <, ==, >=, <=
    - value type : float

- status  : one-character tag at line start
- message : message tag at line end

=== Group classification (Summary Report) ==================

<group> c:<class_tag>                   # classify group by user-defined tag 
                                          base on the violation type

=== Define Message =========================================

mtag:<message_tag>: <message>

